data.description: Check out this spacious home located in the Arrowhead subdivision! This home features 4 beds, 2 baths, plus a bonus room and sits on a .4+/- acre lot. The living room features a modernized fireplace and a great view of the back patio, ideal for entertaining! The living room flows into the kitchen with a breakfast nook. The kitchen has all stainless steel appliances and a huge walk-in pantry. There are sliding barn doors on several of the rooms to add to the rustic design of the home. You'll love the covered patio on the back of the house that overlooks the private yard! The backyard is fenced in and a perfect size for kids & pets. There is a 689+/- sq ft workshop situated in the backyard, which is set up for power with a breaker box & outlets.
